Cyril Delevanti https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cyril_Delevanti 0 Harry Cyril Delevanti (23 February 1889 – 13 December 1975) was an English character actor with a long career in American films. He was sometimes credited as Syril Delevanti. Harry_Cyril_Delevanti ( 23_February_1889 – 13_December_1975 ) was an_English_character_actor with a_long_career in American_films .
